overview.en: Connecting people with all digital assets as its mission and AWARE of Good Token as its slogan, AWARE is creating a distributed search and community platform for blockchain projects and is committed to becoming the super portal of future digital assets.
overview.zh: AWARE先知以“连接人与一切数字资产”为使命，以“好币我先知”为口号，打造全球领先的分布式区块链项目搜索和社群平台，致力于成为未来数字资产的超级入口。
